description:
This course is targeted for people who would like to take Oracle DBA as their career. This course talks about:

  • Oracle DBA Career
  • Expectations from an Oracle DBA
  • Different levels of Oracle DBA
  • What is the Oracle DBA interview pattern
  • Preparing an excellent Oracle DBA resume
ORACLEGENESIS provides free mock interviews and resume preparation services online.
title: Cracking Oracle DBA Interview
